00:04:29.719 --> 00:04:30.909
one last thing i forgot

00:04:30.909 --> 00:04:32.740
the clean shot valve from graco

00:04:32.740 --> 00:04:39.949
if you are using a tip extension this is important
to have

00:04:39.949 --> 00:04:43.379
when you release the trigger on the spray
gun

00:04:43.379 --> 00:04:47.690
it releases paint in a messy fashion without
the valve

00:04:47.690 --> 00:04:54.090
The cleanshot valve knows when you release
the trigger

00:04:54.090 --> 00:04:56.599
and stops the paint at the end of the tip.

